            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                See our Pulse Cascade Splitter™ break down professional tracks in real-time. <strong class="text-pulse-cyan">Reveal production secrets hidden in the mix.</strong>
            </p>
